      "content": "it honestly feels more like i'm just a ghost wandering around. i look at his side of the bed and it's like my soul isn't even in my body anymore. i feel like i'm just going through the motions of a life that ended when he died. everything is so pointless, it's like i'm just waiting for something to happen, but there's nothing left to wait for.",
